abstract: Vodafone ends early stage talks about exchanging assets with cable and wireless company Liberty Global.
lead_paragraph: The ending of the discussions comes as consolidation in Europe’s telecommunications industry is falling under greater scrutiny from the region’s antitrust authorities.

headline.main: Vodafone Ends Talks on a Deal With Liberty Global
